= SDL_SetTextureAlphaMod =
Use this function to set an additional alpha value used in render copy operations.


== Syntax ==
```c++
int SDL_SetTextureAlphaMod(SDL_TextureID textureID,
                           Uint8         alpha)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''textureID'''
|the texture to update
|-
|'''alpha'''
|the source alpha value multiplied into copy operations
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns 0 on success or -1 if the texture is not valid or alpha modulation is not supported; call [[SDL_GetError]]() for more information.

